{"tid":2316793,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone用家比較蠢？研究：Android手機用家平均智商較高IQ達110.3","createTime":"2020-12-08T06:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T11:16:25.000Z","uid":58335,"like":23,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0ef6ac6332cff722552562014109ae2a7126c356","tid":2316793,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T06:18:28.000Z","msg":"不少人常為Android 手機與 iPhone作出比較，最近外國線上賭場遊戲Royal Panda進行研究調查，針對iOS、Android、Windows、Mac等手機和電腦作業系統為研究，結果發現Android用戶平均智商較iPhone用戶高。<br />\n<br />\nRoyal Panda早前與心理學家合作進行研究，針對iOS、Android、Windows、Mac等7 個平台，邀請到1001位用戶進行智商測驗，測驗內容包括語文、數學、邏輯與視覺等部分。<br />\n<br />\n結果發現，Android 系統用戶的IQ平均分為110.3，而iPhone 用戶IQ平均分為102.1，可見Android用家平均智商較高。而電腦系統方面情況相反，macOS用戶平均IQ為108.2 ，比起平均IQ為106.7的Windows 用戶高。<br />\n<br />\n雖然調查報告結果Android用家平均智商較高，但Royal Panda亦指用戶人數比例亦有機會拉低智商，加上測試方式也沒有詳細公佈，各位可以一笑置之不用太介懷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/213230/iphone%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%B6%E6%AF%94%E8%BC%83%E8%A0%A2-%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-android%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%B6%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E6%99%BA%E5%95%86%E8%BC%83%E9%AB%98iq%E9%81%94110-3/2?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_content=link&amp;preview=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail%2F213230%2Fiphone%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%25AF%2594%25E8%25BC%2583%25E8%25A0%25A2-%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6-android%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%259D%2587%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%2595%2586%25E8%25BC%2583%25E9%25AB%2598iq%25E9%2581%2594110-3%2F2%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_content%3Dlink%26preview%3D1&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7Mv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=6bf3da10\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/213230/iphone%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%B6%E6%AF%94%E8%BC%83%E8%A0%A2-%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-android%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E7%94%A8%E5%AE%B6%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E6%99%BA%E5%95%86%E8%BC%83%E9%AB%98iq%E9%81%94110-3/2?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_content=link&amp;preview=1</a>"},{"pid":"b842b70cf7d36bebc28e231ad86f7fc39c6a4316","tid":2316793,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T07:12:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daff349b6ea2b20d7f3193277f7766cebec5361e","tid":2316793,"uid":28801,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T08:44:07.000Z","msg":"android用家包左華為小米未？"},{"pid":"3a177a4d30a12d3db5de2a09e43863c226459c38","tid":2316793,"uid":119667,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"daff349b6ea2b20d7f3193277f7766cebec5361e","tid":2316793,"uid":28801,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T08:44:07.000Z","msg":"android用家包左華為小米未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T08:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16347788aeb398a2b6334699375e1f90482efe34","tid":2316793,"uid":327462,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"daff349b6ea2b20d7f3193277f7766cebec5361e","tid":2316793,"uid":28801,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T08:44:07.000Z","msg":"android用家包左華為小米未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T08:48:33.000Z","msg":"人哋用鴻蒙<br />\n唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8105c7ffb0d053a789196ed3fcb8b6f336e3800d","tid":2316793,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"daff349b6ea2b20d7f3193277f7766cebec5361e","tid":2316793,"uid":28801,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T08:44:07.000Z","msg":"android用家包左華為小米未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:15:38.000Z","msg":"可能計埋都高過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw,咁雙修即係點?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8faa25940754dbffd6cbed7